************************************************************************

          THIS PACKAGE IS SUPERSEDED BY ats2-xprelude

(It did not work very well, anyway.)

************************************************************************


Floating-point support for ATS2/Postiats beyond what is in the
prelude.

In particular, support for binary and decimal floating point types
specified in ISO/IEC TS 18661-3:2015, ‘Floating point extensions for
C: interchange and extended types’.

